Umbono womanyano, ongenabuhlanga necandelo lolimo olunempumelelo olusekwe kwinjongo zeziphamba ezithathu zendlela nokuthabatha inxaxheba, ukhuphiswano nenzuzo nokugcinwa kolawulo lobutyebi.
Lo ngumbono omde oza kulandelwa phantse yonke lenkulungwane ukuzisa inkqubo entsha, enomahluko nengaphezulu yolimo kunale ikhoyo.
