Zonke ezi ngabadlali abanendima ebaluleke kakhulu nabaxumi boyilo lokuphamba oluyilelwe ukusebenzela umxumi wokugqibela, abantu baseMzantsi Afrika ukuphumeza injongo yobomi obungcono babo bonke.
