Apha uRhulumente, ngokwengqondo yamanani akhe aqokelelweyo, asenendima ebalulekileyo ayidlalayo, xeshikweni ezinye iziqalo ezifana nokwakhiwa kutsha nje kwesiXokelelwano seNgqiqo seShishini loLimo naso esiza kukhuthazwa.
