Urhulumente uza kwandisa unkezelo mali kuphando lolimo ukukhuthaza impucuko eqhubekekayo kukhuphiswano nobunkokheli kulwazi, uqhagamshelwano nakulwazi ngobugcisa jikelele ngebhayoloji obubalulekileyo kulimo lwangomso eMzantsi Afrika.
